            "text": "<p>Platinum is one of the rarest and densest precious metals used in fine jewelry. It is naturally white, hypoallergenic, and extremely durable. Unlike white gold, which requires rhodium plating, platinum retains its color for life, making it a popular choice for high-end <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-ring\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"engagement rings\">engagement rings</a> and everyday jewelry</p>",
