        "rich_text_aMiy4L": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Jewelry Type Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Platinum Rings vs Diamond Rings</h3><p>A platinum ring without stones generally costs less than a diamond ring. Once diamonds are introduced, especially larger stones or premium cuts, diamonds dominate the pricing.</p><h3>Platinum Band vs Diamond Stud Earrings</h3><p>A simple platinum band is usually more affordable than diamond studs, which rely heavily on carat weight and quality.</p><h3>Complex Designs</h3><p>Jewelry such as a diamond tennis bracelet tends to be significantly more expensive because it contains multiple high-quality stones, unlike a platinum piece that is priced primarily by metal weight.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
