        "rich_text_ADDTPa": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Expert Insights: Why Prices Differ Between Brands",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h1>Expert Insights: Why Prices Differ Between Brands</h1><p>Luxury brands differ in:</p><ul><li>Craftsmanship<br/></li><li>Diamond sourcing<br/></li><li>Ethical mining<br/></li><li>Product design<br/></li><li>Brand heritage<br/></li></ul><p>These elements often influence final pricing more than raw materials alone.</p>",
