        "rich_text_7bxGmb": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Final Verdict: Platinum or Diamond Which Is More Expensive?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h1>Final Verdict: Platinum or Diamond Which Is More Expensive?</h1><p>In most scenarios, diamonds are more expensive than platinum, especially when comparing higher-carat stones or premium-grade diamonds. Platinum is undeniably valuable, but diamond pricing outpaces it significantly due to rarity, grading, and market demand.</p><p>Your choice ultimately depends on personal preference, purpose, and style. Both materials offer timeless luxury and enduring beauty.</p><p>Discover fine craftsmanship and exceptional quality with Lucira’s premium jewelry collections. Whether you're drawn to the brilliance of diamonds or the timeless elegance of platinum, explore pieces designed to last a lifetime at <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Lucira Jewelry</span></a>.</p>",
